<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-4161] CQL 3.0 does not work in cqlsh with uppercase SELECT</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-4161</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Uppercase SELECT prevents usage of CQL 3.0 features like ORDER BY&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;select * from test ORDER BY number; # works&lt;br/&gt;
SELECT * from test ORDER BY number; # fails&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;cqlsh&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12551208">CASSANDRA-4161</key>
            <summary>CQL 3.0 does not work in cqlsh with uppercase SELECT</summary>
